    public static final class UpgradeOccurrence.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<UpgradeOccurrence.Builder>
implements UpgradeOccurrenceOrBuilder
     An Upgrade Occurrence represents that a specific resource_url could install a
 specific upgrade. This presence is supplied via local sources (i.e. it is
 present in the mirror and the running system has noticed its availability).
 For Windows, both distribution and windows_update contain information for the
 Windows update.
    Protobuf type grafeas.v1.UpgradeOccurrence
